				<h3 id="post-993"><a href="http://www.blog.argatea.com.ar/2009/08/03/argentina-pastores-del-orden/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Argentina: Pastores del orden">Argentina: Pastores del orden</a></h3>
				<small>Lunes, Agosto 3rd, 2009</small>

				<div class="entry">
					<p><!--[endif]--></p>
<table class="MsoTableGrid" style="border: medium none; border-collapse: collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
